Checkbox Field
------------------------------------

Version: 2.0.0
Author: Symphony Team (team@symphony-cms.com)
Build Date: 16 February 2010
Requirements: Symphony 3


Installation
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

1. Upload the 'field_checkbox' folder in this archive to your Symphony 'extensions' folder.

2. Enable it by selecting "Field: Checkbox" and choosing "Enable" from the with-selected menu, then click Apply.

3. You can now add the "Checkbox" field to your sections.